{"tid":1063094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司長：沒有逃犯送大陸　一國兩制遠見","createTime":"2019-03-15T13:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T07:01:12.000Z","uid":47714,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6f4b0859ab832498eb9940a59b7cdf07bc3ab7","tid":1063094,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190309/s00002/1552070211264/陳弘毅-現行移交逃犯安排非漏洞-黃仁龍曾稱沒有逃犯送內地-一國兩制遠見\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190309%2Fs00002%2F1552070211264%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%BC%98%E6%AF%85-%E7%8F%BE%E8%A1%8C%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%9D%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E9%BE%8D%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E9%80%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E9%81%A0%E8%A6%8B&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=67c9f068\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190309%2Fs00002%2F1552070211264%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%BC%98%E6%AF%85-%E7%8F%BE%E8%A1%8C%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%9D%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E9%BE%8D%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E9%80%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E9%81%A0%E8%A6%8B&h=9db49f82\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190309/s00002/1552070211264/陳弘毅-現行移交逃犯安排非漏洞-黃仁龍曾稱沒有逃犯送內地-一國兩制遠見</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】保安局提出修訂《逃犯條例》，稱現時存法律缺陷，不能移交逃犯給內地及台灣等地。基本法委員會委員陳弘毅（圖）指出，現時法律安排不是漏洞，他指一直有人擔心港人移交內地，人身自由等不能得到充分保障，而他亦未有很好的建議可解決此方面問題。2005年時任律政司長黃仁龍則曾公開說，1997年回歸後沒有發生逃犯會被送回內地，指一國兩制構想具遠見，保障香港法治和司法獨立。<br />\n<br />\n黃當年稱基本法落實法治非常成功<br />\n<br />\n一宗在台灣發生的港人謀殺案，引發政府稱要填補制度缺陷，建議修訂《逃犯條例》移交逃犯予內地、台灣等與香港沒簽互助協議地方。據政府新聞公報，黃仁龍2005年11月任律政司長時，曾在新華社前香港分社社長周南在場的紀念《中英聯合聲明》生效20周年午餐會致辭，形容從法律制度和法治方面來說《基本法》落實非常成功，他說不少人在基本法頒布後仍預言1997年後香港會沒落，但「移交香港的逃犯會被送回內地等」等預言全部落空，「一國兩制」構想非常有遠見，而且一直在特區落實執行，「香港的法律制度建基於普通法、法治和司法獨立。雖然跟內地不同，這個制度在新的憲法秩序之下仍然得以全面保存」。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨向黃仁龍查詢，至截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200511/18/P200511170154.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200511%2F18%2FP200511170154.htm&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ec8a8521\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200511/18/P200511170154.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nj3pBLv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNj3pBLv.png&h=c3eeab51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toZPNSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoZPNSd.png&h=c39c045b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WDskEPAOzHA&amp;t=39\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWDskEPAOzHA%26t%3D39&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=cc5cecd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WDskEPAOzHA&amp;t=39</a>"},{"pid":"fbb72507fc9547194f0e041488cf8d44b67c71fd","tid":1063094,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c643ecb15e572f331d617d8c77dd7bb1124fd76c","tid":1063094,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"成班文盲<br />\n移交香港的"},{"pid":"364ca363de361ff51397512ac3c7b50ca43dc124","tid":1063094,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話事啦"},{"pid":"a12cd94b3a788ba73a25b15caebd665802fbd791","tid":10630